items.title: What is this Support Pages tab?
items.text: This is a special section within our app that we update from the internet. This means we can give you information quickly, without you having to update the app.

items.title: What is DeluxeFX Professional Membership?
items.text: It is an annual subscription that unlocks all the video editing filters and tools.
